<div class="title">Shadow People Appear</div>
<div class="substance">Cannabis & Alcohol - Hard</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Moustache+Pete&Exact=1">Moustache Pete</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Moustache Pete. "Shadow People Appear: An Experience with Cannabis & Alcohol - Hard (exp55183)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 25, 2007. erowid.org/exp/55183</div>

<br/>



